          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "I am counting on the Lord; yes, I am counting on him. I have put my hope in his word. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "I am counting on the Lord; yes, I am counting on him. I have put my hope in his word."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
